# Local iOS deploy config. Copy to `.env` (git-ignored) and fill in your values.
# Both are optional: with no device set, the deploy targets the first connected device.

# Your iPhone/iPad UDID or a device-name substring (used by Scripts/build-ios.sh device).
DUNEII_DEVICE=
# Your Apple Developer team ID (device builds / archive).
DUNEII_TEAM=
# Manual-signing provisioning profile NAME (or UUID) for com.lonelybytes.duneii. Device builds use manual
# signing (no on-the-fly profile minting — that network call hangs headless), so this must name a profile
# already installed for your team that includes your device. Find it in Xcode ▸ Settings ▸ Accounts ▸
# (team) ▸ Manage Profiles, or ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/UserData/Provisioning Profiles.
DUNEII_PROFILE=
